#X text 55 64 For those looking for a pure vanilla exponential envelope again \, we can use [vline~] with a toggle that behaves like a gate into [slop~]. For san "ASR" envelope triggered by a gate \, it's pretty simple \, just set it according to the attack/release period. Belowe we convert them to frequency values for the filter.;
